 @dev Interface for interacting with the TwoWheels2RentRenter contract.

 @param _lenderWhitelist Address of the LenderWhitelist contract.
@dev Deploy a BikeRent contract for the renter.
@notice Remove a renter from the whitelist.

 @param _address Address to be blacklisted.

devdoc.details: This contract manages a whitelist of renters and their associated BikeRent contracts. It allows renters to be added to the whitelist and to deploy BikeRent contracts. The contract owner can add and remove renters from the blacklist.

params._TW2RLenderNFT: Address of the Lender NFT contract.
params._W2R: Address of the W2R token contract.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params._address: Address to be removed from the blacklist.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

devdoc.title: RenterWhitelist

addToBlacklist(address).notice: Add an address to the blacklist.

constructor.notice: Constructor to set the required addresses for the contract.

removeAddressFromWhitelist().notice: Remove a renter from the whitelist.

removeFromBlacklist(address).notice: Remove an address from the blacklist.

renounceOwnership().notice: Prevent renouncing ownership of this contract.

setRenterInfoAndMint(string,string).notice: Add a renter to the whitelist, set Renter struct and call mintNFT.
